The '''Crotok''' were a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Alien/Legends|alien]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. This species' members included [[Unidentified pilot (Kizbon's Box)|the pilot]] of a [[Helix-class light interceptor]], ''[[Kizbon's Box]]'', targeted by a gang of [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] led by [[Larken]]. The pirates mistakenly thought the pilot would be unarmed, but much to their surprise, the Crotok managed to outfight them using [[Proton torpedo/Legends|proton torpedoes]].<ref name="ABGTAS">{{JournalCite|5|A Buyer's Guide to Alternative Starships}}</ref>

